column2: SELECT    s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, ife.ra as ifeRA, ife.dec as ifeDEC, StarformingPort.logMass, StarformingPort.age, StarformingPort.SFR,   PassivePort.logMass as logMass_passive, PassivePort.age as age_passive, PassivePort.SFR as sfr_passive, PCAWiscBC0#.mstellar_median as logmass_pcaB0# into mydb.ife_stellarMassAllTable_dr1# from mydb.for_bpt as ife      CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq(ife.ra,ife.dec, #) AS near    JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID=s.specObjID   JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort AS StarformingPort ON StarformingPort.specObjID = near.specObjID   JOIN stellarMassPassivePort AS PassivePort ON PassivePort.specObjID = near.specObjID   JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS PCAWiscBC0# ON PCAWiscBC0#.specObjID = near.specObjID      WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=#
